primary.context: Caller had questions regarding a maintenance bill and ownership info
primary.detail: Agent verified the caller and provided the address and owner name on file.

steps: Agent identified the intent as maintenance billing.
Agent performed account lookup via phone number.
Agent verified the caller's identity (name and state).
Agent provided the address on file upon request.
Agent provided the owner name and contract details upon request.
Caller confirmed no further assistance was needed.

clarifications.note: Initial name provided didn't match record exactly

actions.detail: Verified Valerie Creo in New Jersey

insights.summary: The caller successfully verified their identity and obtained specific contract details including the address and owner name on file for their maintenance bill.
insights.verbatim: The owner on file for Vacation Village at Williamsburg, unit two one nine, contract number three eight one nine three four, is Valerie Creo.
